&lt;p class=&quot;_markdownText_1ni73_69 _paragraph_1ni73_65&quot;&gt;Zipline is looking for an exceptional Executive Assistant to support Jo Mardall, our Chief Hardware Officer, and CJ Moore, our Head of Autonomy. Together, Jo and CJ lead some of the most technically complex and operationally critical work at Zipline: aircraft reliability, hardware execution, flight software, autonomy, release readiness, fleet health, and the systems that allow Zipline to scale safely.&lt;/p&gt;
