&lt;p class=&quot;_markdownText_1ni73_69 _paragraph_1ni73_65&quot;&gt;The right person for this role is highly organized, calm under pressure, technically curious, and comfortable operating in ambiguity. You do not need to be an engineer, but you do need to be able to follow technical conversations well enough to understand what matters, who owns what, what needs to happen next, and when something needs to be escalated.&lt;/p&gt;
