&lt;h2 class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Own end-to-end daily flight test campaign execution - Acting as Remote Pilot in Command for Zipline’s Autonomous Aircraft - executing mission profiles, feature testing, and fault injection testing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Validate functionality through repeatable ground and flight test procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Troubleshoot and repair software and hardware issues on-site to return aircraft to flight&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Summarize test results: provide qualitative and quantitative analysis on the performance of an aircraft as it completes its mission - comparing to a set of expected outcomes provided by engineering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Escalate flight performance anomalies to engineering and safety, driving discussion towards resolution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Enforce and improve site safety: manage risks for prototype flights, run briefings and debriefs, and refine SOPs to reduce repeat failures.&lt;/li&gt;
