&lt;p&gt;Zipline’s delivery network depends on clear decisions, reliable operating data, and effective handoffs among Commercial, Operations, Product, Data, Finance, and field teams. As an Operations Ghostbuster, you will find recurring friction in those workflows and build practical systems that help teams execute.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an owner role, not a coordination role. You will prioritize problems by business impact, delivery-network risk, and operating priorities; diagnose root causes; ship fixes; and measure improvements in speed, conversion, decision quality, and execution reliability.&lt;/p&gt;
