&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify high-impact bottlenecks in commercial, operations, and field workflows, including manual handoffs, unclear ownership, missing metrics, stalled decisions, and weak follow-through.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prioritize workstreams using business impact, delivery-network risk, and operating priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Turn ambiguous problems into scoped workstreams with accountable owners, milestones, operating mechanisms, and measurable success criteria.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build dashboards, automations, trackers, and workflows that resolve immediate friction and can scale with the business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own workflow improvements end to end, from diagnosis and stakeholder alignment through implementation, iteration, adoption, and performance review.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner across Commercial, Operations, Product, Data, Finance, and field teams to improve execution across Zipline’s delivery network.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use operating data to measure changes in cycle time, conversion, decision quality, follow-through, and execution performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
